{"tid":2234913,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警察涉隱瞞離婚狀況 霸佔宿舍15年被控欺詐","createTime":"2020-10-08T08:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T17:29:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":521,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"68717446ab352224234310987e195a188372d093","tid":2234913,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"50歲警務人員被指向警隊隱瞞已與妻子離婚，15年來一直霸佔警隊編配的荃灣綠楊新邨警察宿舍，被控一項欺詐罪，今於西九龍裁判法院提堂。裁判官將案件押後至下月19日，以候辯方索取文件。被告獲准保釋，其間不准接觸控方證人，包括其同僚及上司。<br />\n<br />\n被告李德明，控罪書上只描述他報稱任職公務員，沒有列明職級，現居於荃灣另一屋苑。他被控於2005年1月22日至2020年7月13日間，意圖欺詐並藉欺騙，即向香港警務處隱瞞其離婚狀況，而誘使警務處在李不合資格下，繼續向他分配位於綠楊新邨的部門宿舍，導致李獲得利益或使特區政府蒙受不利。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：WKCC3409/20】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/JLSUM6L6IFEODKR5JE5OBCDM4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FJLSUM6L6IFEODKR5JE5OBCDM4U%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5BZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=f0ad5d83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FJLSUM6L6IFEODKR5JE5OBCDM4U%2F&h=d4466f59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/JLSUM6L6IFEODKR5JE5OBCDM4U/</a>"},{"pid":"4b7fa53151b3bd00878a2602f08bb6162813d25b","tid":2234913,"uid":201359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57120758f2da6de12dfa785c86f6854e114d7c44","tid":2234913,"uid":11291,"like":133,"dislike":0,"score":133,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:57:03.000Z","msg":"偷呃拐騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10514b38e77ad600079c218b49a500bb1ad335fd","tid":223491